  m_text: This project is a simple 3D Time Attack Racing Game developed using Unity
    for Windows platforms. Players can choose their car and track, race against a
    time limit, and aim to finish within the given time while setting their best
    record. The game features checkpoint-based progression and encourages players
    to improve their speed and racing skills.
